    "entity_count": 60,
    "assumption_notice": "The tesla_custom domain.suffix spellings here are CONFIRMED by source-read (research 2026-07-03 §5, alandtse/tesla type-string naming), NOT corpus-captured — we hold no live tesla_custom install. Values/units are inherited from the fleet corpus. charging_status is a boolean binary_sensor.charging (on/off), not a status string. Energy-site entities are matched by function-slug substring (energy.ts), independent of dialect, so they keep their fleet-shaped ids.",
    "notes": "Exercises AC4 of Story 5.11: the whole card rendered against the costly distinct dialect (tesla_custom) to confirm no fleet-shaped assumptions leak into the UI. Cover/lock/aperture reads route through the dialect normalizers (Story 5.11 remediation); charge state goes through normalizeChargingState. Synthetic data only — no Tesla art/trade-dress."
